dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Antioch South & Brentwood quadrangles, Contra Costa County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Antioch South and Brentwood quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Antioch South, CA 1953, DMA 1659 IV NE - Series V895, Photorevised 1980; Brentwood, CA 1978, AMS 1659 I NW - Series V895."
"Contour interval Antioch South quadrangle 20 feet ; Brentwood quadrangle 20 and 5 feet."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
